4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge to become cybersecurity specialists and protect digital assets. The program provides a comprehensive foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside practical skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. It includes 3 live online classes per week over 16 weeks, with a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate upon successful completion. The course is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop